Creating a Successful Office Team

After completing this module, you will be able to:
Describe employee turnover, reasons for high turnover and engagement 
Discuss the role of a team, culture, values, how to manage teams and team communication 
Recall the content of employee engagement and the role of leadership 
Summarise guidance on how to manage a team meeting and to develop team processes
Identify team members using 'The Belbin' team roles
Define and describe the 9 team roles according to 'The Belbin' method 

